Capabilities
Choose products that advance the world of health and help improve the safety and cost of healthcare for generations to come
BD offers a wide range of capabilities that help healthcare providers advance the world of health by improving medical discovery, diagnostics and the delivery of care. Whether you are a researcher in the lab, a nurse handling hazardous drugs or a physician prescribing medication—from anesthesia delivery to syringes and needles, our capabilities can help enhance outcomes, lower costs, increase efficiencies, improve safety and expand access to health for health systems all around the world.










